node.text: Our 7th & final Ford car to help celebrate 70 years of @nhra racing is a glimpse into the future. The all-electric Mustang Cobra Jet 1400 made its debut in 2020 & set an #NHRA EV record run of 8.12 at 171.97 mph in June 2021. A new EV class is on NHRA's horizon for 2022. #TBT

node.text: Ford CEO Jim Farley believes in treating customers like family. So when he received a note from a friend of a long-time @ford customer asking for a special wish, he asked Ford Performance to help. And we're glad he did.
